{{Infobox dungeon |name = Memorial Hill |image = [[File:Memorial Hill.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Memorial Hill. |tokens = 950,000 |location = West of Akala Outskirts/East of Route 9. }}
'''Memorial Hill''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Alola]]. It initially has 121 tiles arranged in a 11x11 square, including 11 chest tiles, 41 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 13,286,024 HP.
